-- Abbott Sues Mylan Over Plans to Market Copies of Simcor Cholesterol Drug
-- Phil Milford
-- 2010-06-29T13:25:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/abbott-sues-mylan-over-plans-to-market-copies-of-simcor-cholesterol-drug.html

          
          
             Abbott Laboratories sued generic
drugmaker Mylan Inc. in federal court in Delaware, alleging
infringement of eight patents and seeking an order to block
generic copies of the cholesterol drug Simcor.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Phil Milford in Wilmington, Delaware, at 
 pmilford@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        